text: Ünver Beşergil (born 25 March 1938) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
